ever met anybody like you before, sir.

50:17.782 --> 50:22.151
Really? Over 1,800 of my brothers
have come before me.

50:22.219 --> 50:25.519
1,800? Imagine the grocery bills.

50:25.589 --> 50:27.580
[both laugh]

50:30.995 --> 50:35.296
Have you ever noticed that everything
seems wonderful at Christmas?

50:36.867 --> 50:41.668
Uh, in all honesty, spirit, no.

50:43.140 --> 50:46.075
Perhaps I've never understood
about Christmas.

50:46.143 --> 50:50.171
Before this day is done,
you will understand.

50:50.247 --> 50:52.113
Oh. [laughs]

50:52.183 --> 50:54.117
Oh, no! Oh, no!

50:56.487 --> 50:59.752
We shall go out into the world.

51:02.626 --> 51:05.027
I suppose you enjoyed that?

51:05.096 --> 51:06.621
Of course.

51:11.734 --> 51:16.296
May I welcome you
to Christmas morning?

51:16.372 --> 51:18.101
[laughs]

