54:06.609 --> 54:08.543
Having Christmas with friends.

54:09.578 --> 54:11.068
Hey, look. Fruit.

54:11.146 --> 54:14.241
Well, now, we've had the plum pudding
and sung the carols.

54:14.316 --> 54:16.307
- What now, my lovelies?
- A game, Fred.

54:16.385 --> 54:18.547
Yeah, we must have a game at Christmas.

54:18.621 --> 54:22.114
- Do people play games at Christmas?
- I love games.

54:22.191 --> 54:24.853
Say, do you know that fruit is wax?

54:24.927 --> 54:28.363
Oh, yeah,
I wondered about the texture. Yeuch!

54:28.430 --> 54:31.559
- Let's play "Yes and No."
- Oh, wonderful game.

54:31.634 --> 54:34.695
Yah! That's a great game. I'll be it.

54:34.770 --> 54:37.535
Yes, let Fred be it.
He always thinks of good things.

54:37.606 --> 54:40.007
I do have a good one, Clara. Guess.

54:40.075 --> 54:42.066
Is it vegetable?

54:42.144 --> 54:43.669
- [Fred] No.
- [Clara] Mineral?

54:43.746 --> 54:45.145
- No.
- Animal, then?

54:45.214 --> 54:47.114
- What else?
- What else, indeed.

54:47.182 --> 54:49.412
- Is it found on a farm?
- Never.

54:49.485 --> 54:51.180
- In the city?
- Usually.

54:51.253 --> 54:53.483
Does it pull a hansom cab?

54:53.555 --> 54:55.080
Certainly not.

54:55.157 --> 54:56.886
How about a dog?

54:56.959 --> 54:57.949
No.

54:58.027 --> 54:59.153
- A cat?
- A cat?

54:59.228 --> 55:02.562
- I said it first.
- No.

55:02.631 --> 55:05.191
Wait, is this an unwanted creature?

55:05.267 --> 55:07.463
- Often.
- A mouse?

55:07.536 --> 55:08.765
- No.
- A rat?

55:08.837 --> 55:10.931
- You called?
- A cockroach.

55:11.006 --> 55:11.996
No.

55:12.074 --> 55:13.599
- A leech?
- It's too wonderful.

55:13.676 --> 55:16.668
Wait, I know.
An unwanted creature,

55:16.745 --> 55:19.214
but not a rat, a leech,
or a cockroach?

55:19.281 --> 55:20.339
Then what?

55:20.416 --> 55:22.748
- What?
- It's Ebenezer Scrooge.

55:22.818 --> 55:23.808
Yes.

55:23.886 --> 55:26.150
- [all laugh]
- Wonderful.

55:27.222 --> 55:29.919
[female friend] That's a killer.

55:37.166 --> 55:40.136
Come, there is much to see.

55:40.202 --> 55:43.172
